summary: This is a calendar invitation for a grand jury session related to the Ghislaine Maxwell superseding indictment, scheduled for March 29, 2021, in Manhattan. It lists the organizer as USANYS (U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York) and includes attendees from the FBI and NYPD.

events.title: Grand Jury Session for Maxwell Superseding Indictment
events.description: A grand jury session is scheduled to take place regarding the superseding indictment against Ghislaine Maxwell.

keyFacts: A grand jury session related to Ghislaine Maxwell's superseding indictment was scheduled for March 29, 2021, from 2:00 PM to 5:00 PM.
The event was organized by USANYS (U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York).
Attendees included representatives from the FBI and NYPD, though specific individual names are not provided in the text.
The calendar invitation was created on March 5, 2021, indicating planning for legal proceedings in the Maxwell case.
The document is an external email calendar invitation, showing coordination between federal and local law enforcement for grand jury proceedings.
